---
source: tests/recorder_persistence.rs
assertion: recorder commands append to and read from the persisted event store
schema:
  start: ee.recorder.start.v1
  event: ee.recorder.event.v1
  finish: ee.recorder.finish.v1
  import_plan: ee.recorder.import_plan.v1
contracts:
  - recorder events persist with deterministic run IDs, event IDs, and sequence numbers
  - malformed payloads are rejected without partially persisted events
  - list filters by run ID and time window
  - append-only event rows preserve event hashes and chain continuity
  - dry-run imports avoid recorder store mutation
evidence:
  - recorder_store
  - recorder_events.event_id
  - recorder_events.sequence
  - recorder_events.event_hash
  - recorder_events.chain_status
  - RecorderImportPlan
fixtures:
  - tests/fixtures/golden/recorder/gate17_event_response.json.golden
  - tests/fixtures/golden/recorder/gate17_import_plan.json.golden
  - tests/recorder_persistence.rs
